Package divisor

Class ReadPairs

  • java.lang.Object
    • divisor.ReadPairs
  • public class ReadPairs
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will take a file and read the integers inside it, creating an IntPair ArrayList that will be used in GreatestDivisor

    The only method that can be called externally is createPairs(java.io.File).

    The other method, createInts(java.io.File), is called internally by createPairs(java.io.File)

    Author:
    Dalton
